\frac{d }{d r} \mathrm{arctanh}^2{ \frac{r}{\sqrt{5 r^2 + 4}} } = 2 \frac{\mathrm{arctanh}{ \frac{r}{\sqrt{5 r^2 + 4}} }}{(1+r^2) \sqrt{5 r^2 + 4}} . 
